---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import SectionLabel from '../../components/SectionLabel.astro';
---

<Base
  title="CalmAir"
  description="CalmAir measures real turbulence with your iPhone's sensors and tells you what it really was - fully offline, no accounts, no data collected."
>
  <section>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-page px-8 py-section">
      <SectionLabel label="calmair" />
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-page-h1 text-text-primary max-w-prose">
        Turbulence, measured. Fear, shrunk.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-card-body text-text-secondary max-w-prose">
        CalmAir is an iOS app for anxious flyers. It uses your iPhone's motion and barometer
        sensors to measure real turbulence in flight, and reassures you with plain, factual
        comparisons - "that bump was 0.3g, about the same as braking at a traffic light." It
        also has guided breathing and a short library of calm explainer cards. It works 100%
        offline, in flight mode, with no accounts and no network calls, ever.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-page px-8 section-divider"></div>

  <section>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-page px-8 py-section grid md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] gap-x-10 gap-y-10">
      <SectionLabel label="support" />
      <div class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2 max-w-3xl">
        <a href="mailto:stewart@stewart-burton.com?subject=CalmAir%20support" class="card p-6 group">
          <span class="mono-label">email</span>
          <p class="mt-3 text-card text-text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">
            stewart@stewart-burton.com <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-card-body text-text-secondary">
            For bugs, questions, or anything about the app. I read every message and reply
            within a working day.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/calmair/privacy" class="card p-6 group">
          <span class="mono-label">privacy</span>
          <p class="mt-3 text-card text-text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">
            Privacy policy <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-card-body text-text-secondary">
            CalmAir collects nothing. Here's exactly what that means.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
